{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"83db732d9f","title":"对周恩来在政协二届二次会议上的政治报告稿的修改","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"b068a20ff3","index":0,"year":1956,"month":1,"day":null,"articleId":"83db732d9f"}],"tags":[{"id":"523bb79e8f","name":"周恩来","type":"人物"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji36","name":"毛泽东全集第36卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/36-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji36":{"comments":[{"id":"02c9b44cd2","publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"83db732d9f","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"本篇一至三是毛泽东对周恩来1956年1月30日在全国政协二届二次会议上政治报告稿所作的修改。文中用宋体学排印的是毛泽东加写和改写的文字。"}],"contents":[{"id":"acdcef9280","type":"title","text":"对周恩来在政协二届二次会议上的政治报告稿的修改”","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"83db732d9f"},{"id":"02c9b44cd2","type":"paragraph","text":"我们要求和平，但是如果国际侵略集团把战争强加在我们头上的话，我们也并不惧怕战争。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"83db732d9f"},{"id":"0a5b63e7eb","type":"subtitle","text":"皖","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"83db732d9f"},{"id":"825cb792ff","type":"paragraph","text":"我国政府一年来曾经再三指出：除了用战争方式解放台湾以外，还存在着用和平方式解放台湾的可能性。这样，我国大陆人民和台湾人民就有一种共同的爱国的责任，这就是除了积极准备在必要的时候用战争方式解放台湾以外，努力争取用和平方式解放台湾。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"83db732d9f"}],"page":{"id":"b3eff9eb83","publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"83db732d9f","start":203,"end":203}}}},"__N_SSG":true}